
Overview of noun scallywag

The noun scallywag has 3 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                    
1. scalawag, scallywag -- (a white Southerner who supported Reconstruction policies after the American Civil War (usually for self-interest))
2. rogue, knave, rascal, rapscallion, scalawag, scallywag, varlet -- (a deceitful and unreliable scoundrel)
3. imp, scamp, monkey, rascal, rapscallion, scalawag, scallywag -- (one who is playfully mischievous)
